{
  "texts": [
    "There are a variety of methods and metrics for evaluating the performance of deep-learning models.",
    "Choosing the appropriate metric for a given problem is crucial to ensure that it accurately captures the clinically relevant aspects of the task.",
    "A recent study proposed a framework called Metrics Reloaded, which provides a tool to guide researchers through the process of choosing the right validation metrics for their DL model 57.",
    "The two most important metrics for brain tumor segmentation are the Dice score and the Hausdorff distance (HD).",
    "The Dice score measures the overlap between the predicted segmentation and the ground truth segmentation."
  ]
}